    "Figure 1 illustrates the basic framework of the TCN model being applied to this study.",
    "The TCN model is based on a 1 -D fully convolutional network (FCN), where each hidden layer shares the same length as the input layer.",
    "The advantages of TCN can be seen in three aspects: causal convolution, dilated convolution, and residual block.",
